Subject: Re: [T2] Will Plywood Sheets Fit in a Bus

I just measured my '71.  48-1/4 just above the corner radius at the load
floor and 48-1/2 at the belt line.

You can get a sheet in there, but it has to be aligned just _so_ to get it
in!

George

